Mexico ' s Camesa plans single share series . Grupo Industrial Camesa , maker of steel cable and fluorspar miner , plans to combine its A and B series shares into a single share series , Mexican brokerage Finamex reported Thursday . " Creating a single series , with 306 , 503 , 960 shares outstanding , will improve liquidity and facilitate the participation of foreign investors , " Finamex said . The company now has 156 , 317 , 000 A shares and 150 , 186 , 960 free - subscription B shares , Finamex said . It gave no details of when the share combination would take place . Camesa officials were not immediately available to comment . ( ( - - Chris Aspin , Mexico City newsroom ( 525 ) 7289530 ) ) 
